    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point for a value-focused buyer. It presents as a straightforward, honest car with plenty of usable life for the right owner, whether you need basic transportation, a backup vehicle, or a smart project. A compelling opportunity to get behind the wheel without overspending.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little runabout with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showroom car, but if you want something affordable for a project, parts, or a budget-friendly set of wheels, this one could be a great fit. Straightforward sale from someone who loves cars and believes in being upfront \u2014 come have a look and see if it suits what you need.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with a strong mechanical foundation and plenty of upside for the next owner. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels composed enough to be a worthwhile driver-level restoration or budget performance build. Cosmetically it shows its age and needs attention, but the hard-to-find major components are there, making this a great candidate for someone who values mechanical substance over cosmetics. A straightforward, honest car with real potential.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs and gets the job done. Used, rough, priced right. Good project, work car, or cheap daily. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough for the right buyer, this car has the kind of lived-in character you can\u2019t fake and plenty of story left to tell. It\u2019s an affordable way to get into something with real presence\u2014perfect for a hands-on owner, a project-minded driver, or anyone who sees opportunity where others just see age. If you\u2019ve been looking for a budget-friendly ride with personality and potential, this one invites you to make it your own.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical budget-minded choice for someone seeking inexpensive transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and will appeal best to a buyer who values low entry cost and potential over perfection, but it still offers a lot of value at this price point. A smart buy for the right owner looking for dependable basics without a big investment.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car that can still get the job done? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little vehicle with plenty of life left for the right buyer. A great option for someone who wants inexpensive transportation, a project, or a handy spare to have around. If you\u2019re after something affordable and straightforward, this could be a really solid fit.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with solid enthusiast potential. This car presents as a usable platform for someone who appreciates mechanical simplicity and honest character. The powertrain starts, runs, and moves under its own power, and it has the kind of straightforward, analog feel that makes it a great candidate for a budget build, weekend wrenching, or restoration path. Expect cosmetic wear, age-related imperfections, and the usual needs that come with a car in this bracket, but the bones are there for the right buyer. If you want an affordable entry point into a capable platform with room to improve, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
